OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784612872
OL,3,CBurnham unveils tax cut to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' for struggling families
OL,6,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham has
OL,7,Frevealed his plan to "bring back hope"
OL,8,Ffor families struggling with cost of
OL,9,Fliving as he announced announced a tax
OL,10,Fcut for household electricity bills.
OL,12,FThe Government said on Tuesday it
OL,13,Fwould remove VAT from domestic
OL,14,Felectricity bills from October 1,
OL,15,Fadding the measure will be funded by
OL,16,Fsavings from the cancelled digital ID
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@fO]
