OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784612872
OL,3,CBurnham unveils tax cut to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' for struggling families
OL,6,FMr Burnham said: "Westminster has not
OL,7,Fbeen working for people for too long,
OL,8,Fwith families struggling with the cost
OL,9,Fof living.
OL,11,F"That needs to change. I said I wanted
OL,12,Fto give people breathing space, and
OL,13,Fthat's what I'm announcing on my
OL,14,Fsecond day as Prime Minister.
OL,16,F"We're taking immediate action to cut
OL,17,Ftaxes on energy bills, put more money
OL,18,Fin people's pockets and bring back
OL,19,Fhope."
OL,26,@nD@ROUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
