OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784612872
OL,3,CBurnham unveils tax cut to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' for struggling families
OL,6,FIt is estimated that the change will
OL,7,Freduce the annual Ofgem price cap by
OL,8,Faround #45 from October, with
OL,9,Fsuppliers expected to pass savings on
OL,10,Fto their customers.
OL,12,FChancellor John Healey said: "For too
OL,13,Flong, too many people have struggled
OL,14,Fwith the cost of living.
OL,16,F"Today's energy tax cut will give
OL,17,Ffamilies some breathing room on bills,
OL,18,Fand provide some reassurance this
OL,19,Fwinter.
OL,26,@tD@^OUxD@AOU
