OL,3,CBurnham unveils tax cut to 'bring back
OL,4,Chope' for struggling families
OL,6,FHe continued: "This measure is funded
OL,7,Fthis year from cancelling the Digital
OL,8,FID programme, and it will help bring
OL,9,Fdown inflation while supporting
OL,10,Fhouseholds in every postcode."
